#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.47"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.47:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Muṇḍarājavagga"
msgstr "5. With King Muṇḍa"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: pañcadhanasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Dhanasutta"
msgstr "47. Wealth"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, dhanāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five kinds of wealth."

msgctxt "an5.47:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.47:1.3"
msgid "Saddhādhanaṃ, sīladhanaṃ, sutadhanaṃ, cāgadhanaṃ, paññādhanaṃ."
msgstr "The wealth of faith, ethics, learning, generosity, and wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, saddhādhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of faith?"

msgctxt "an5.47:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako saddho hoti, saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ:"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has faith in the Realized One’s awakening:"

msgctxt "an5.47:2.3"
msgid "‘itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "an5.47:2.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, saddhādhanaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the wealth of faith."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, sīladhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of ethics?"

msgctxt "an5.47:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit "
"sexual misconduct, lie, or take alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an5.47:3.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sīladhanaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the wealth of ethics."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, sutadhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of learning?"

msgctxt "an5.47:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako bahussuto hoti … pe … diṭṭhiyā suppaṭividdho."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is very learned, remembering and keeping what "
"they’ve learned. These teachings are good in the beginning, good in the "
"middle, and good in the end, meaningful and well-phrased, describing a "
"spiritual practice that’s totally full and pure. They are very learned in "
"such teachings, remembering them, reciting them, mentally scrutinizing them, "
"and comprehending them theoretically."

msgctxt "an5.47:4.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sutadhanaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the wealth of learning."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:5.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, cāgadhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of generosity?"

#. VAR: vosaggarato → vossaggarato (s1-3, pts1, c1)
msgctxt "an5.47:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"muttacāgo payatapāṇi vosaggarato yācayogo dānasaṃvibhāgarato."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple lives at home rid of the stain of stinginess, "
"freely generous, open-handed, loving to let go, committed to charity, loving "
"to give and to share."

msgctxt "an5.47:5.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, cāgadhanaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the wealth of generosity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:6.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, paññādhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of wisdom?"

msgctxt "an5.47:6.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako paññavā hoti, udayatthagāminiyā paññāya "
"samannāgato ariyāya nibbedhikāya sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is wise. They have the wisdom of arising and "
"passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending "
"of suffering."

msgctxt "an5.47:6.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, paññādhanaṃ."
msgstr "This is called the wealth of wisdom."

msgctxt "an5.47:6.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca dhanānīti."
msgstr "These are the five kinds of wealth."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.54"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:7.1"
msgid "Yassa saddhā tathāgate,"
msgstr "Whoever has faith in the Realized One,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:7.2"
msgid "acalā suppatiṭṭhitā;"
msgstr "unwavering and well grounded;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:7.3"
msgid "Sīlañca yassa kalyāṇaṃ,"
msgstr "whose ethical conduct is good,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:7.4"
msgid "ariyakantaṃ pasaṃsitaṃ."
msgstr "praised and loved by the noble ones;"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:8.1"
msgid "Saṅghe pasādo yassatthi,"
msgstr "who has confidence in the Saṅgha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:8.2"
msgid "ujubhūtañca dassanaṃ;"
msgstr "and correct view:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:8.3"
msgid "Adaliddoti taṃ āhu,"
msgstr "they’re said to be prosperous,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:8.4"
msgid "amoghaṃ tassa jīvitaṃ."
msgstr "their life is not in vain."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an5.47:9.1"
msgid "Tasmā saddhañca sīlañca,"
msgstr "So let the wise devote themselves"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:9.2"
msgid "pasādaṃ dhammadassanaṃ;"
msgstr "to faith, ethical behavior,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:9.3"
msgid "Anuyuñjetha medhāvī,"
msgstr "confidence, and insight into the teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.47:9.4"
msgid "saraṃ buddhāna sāsanan”ti."
msgstr "remembering the instructions of the Buddhas.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.47:9.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
